node.text: She is the sweetest and smilely big girl chef that i’ve seen!

Presenting the ‘HAPPY’ Pizza Sophie made for her bro ❤️ She knows Ian loves eating pizza & was excited to handmade one for him, for snack today🥰 ⁣
⁣
Created a twist in the pizza base using @maggi_sg noodles! Added his favourite toppings - pineapple, mushroom, cheese, capsicum 😋 Easy!⁣
⁣
We have been cooking & baking a lot these days! Maggi has came up with lotsa interesting recipes (swipe to see) Go try out :) ⁣
⁣
⁣
⁣
#siblinglove #CooktheDifferencewithMAGGI #madcravingsSG #sgfoodie #foodiesg #masterchefjunior
wow such creative idea to use noodles as pizza base, nice one!

@ines.adalays haha my son love it too! 😋
Saw a lotta pple doing this pizza base, I absolutely need to try! Also cos I like maggi noodles 😆❤️
Such a cute dish u made 💖
So cute and sweet leh yr daughter 😍 some siblings fight like crazy 😂
So sweet cook suprise for didi💕
So creative and the pizza so cute 😍😍😍
She has a very beautiful smile😍
She is the sweetest and smilely big girl chef that i’ve seen!
